\par\pard\plain \tx720\ql\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 In conclusion, \\cref\{tab:atomic-class-transcriptions\} specifies valid class transcriptions for all atomic correspondences between atomic classes. Unfortunately, two out of five cases prohibit a transcription, a third is rather broad in its transcription, and last but not least, a concept seldom live alone in its ontology.}
